GSN.definition: when in a game and [you beat] some new players or you just beat some [really good] players you can use this to say [everything] for you. while typing 3 letters. GSN (GET SPANKED NOOB) noob= new player

Gurkel.definition:
Gurkel (Gir - Kell)

A nerdy, geeky, girl. Not unlike [Steve Urkel] of tv fame. But a girl.

"Hey man, you see that Gurkel [over there]? What a nerd"

"Hey, I saw you started dating that Gurkel from Dennys. Pfffft"

"I'm a gurkel, [nobody loves me]"
